  %x% as.matrix diag diag<- diff t
Undocumented S4 methods:
  \S4method{coerce}{ANY,array} \S4method{coerce}{ANY,call}
  \S4method{coerce}{ANY,character} \S4method{coerce}{ANY,complex}
